      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STIFLER (4) is a talented type who notched his 12th career success when too good (16.77) at this track last time. Has an impeccable record here at this journey. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can continue the winning form. LET'S GO SAM (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (17.28) at this track behind STIFLER in a Invitation. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Hard to beat again. YVONNE'S PICK (6) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 4.5 lengths back in third (17.05) at this track in a Invitation over 300m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from four starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. MY MUM'S VALUE (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
